And that actually wraps
our day, our Developer Day

00:38:40.980 --> 00:38:41.780
here for Google.

00:38:41.780 --> 00:38:43.890
Thank you so much
for joining us.

00:38:43.890 --> 00:38:46.230
And hopefully you
all are walking away

00:38:46.230 --> 00:38:48.810
with a little gem of wisdom.

00:38:48.810 --> 00:38:50.190
And enjoy the rest of your week.

